channel.title: Orphaned case problem
channel.description:
Hi,
I am getting an error with some code in Applet_Sub1.java. I'm using Bulby 508. It says:
[code] .\files\Applet_Sub1.java:228: orphaned case case 3101: ^ [/code]
This is the code: [code] case 3101: class19.anInt330 = 14998;//inventory/drop model class19.anInt336 = 738;//model zoom class19.anInt389 = 245;//modelRotation1 class19.anInt395 = 80;// model rotation 2 class19.anInt358 = -2;// model offset 1 class19.anInt391 = 3;// model offset 2 class19.anInt390 = 14997;//Male model id class19.aRSString_362 = Class112.method1668(43, "Dragon claws");//Item Name break; [/code]
Obviously, I'm trying to add dragon claws. Can someone please tell me what's wrong?
